Derek Nimmo https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Derek_Nimmo 0 Derek Robert Nimmo (19 September 1930 – 24 February 1999) was an English character actor, producer and author. He was particularly associated with upper class "silly-ass" roles, and clerical roles.
